## Component Patterns

### Card
```tsx
<motion.article
  whileHover={{ y: -2, transition: { duration: 0.2 } }}
  className="group rounded-2xl border border-border bg-card-background p-6 transition-colors hover:border-accent/40"
>
```

### Section wrapper
```tsx
<section className="py-24">
  <div className="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4 sm:px-6">
    {/* content */}
  </div>
</section>
```

### Tag / Badge
```tsx
<span className="inline-flex items-center rounded-full border border-border bg-background px-3 py-1 text-xs font-medium text-text-secondary">
  React
</span>
```

### Divider
```tsx
<hr className="border-border" />
```

